<!DOCTYPE html>
<html prefix="og: http://ogp.me/ns#">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %></title>
</head>

<body>
    <canvas id="canvas"></canvas>
    <div id="preloader">
        <div class="half-placeholder"></div>
        <div id="upper-half"></div>
        <div id="progress-bar-wrapper">
            <div class="progress-bar-placeholder"></div>
            <div id="progress-bar"></div>
            <div class="progress-bar-placeholder"></div>
        </div>
        <div id="lower-half"></div>
        <div class="half-placeholder"></div>
    </div>
    <div id="wrapper">

        <div id="headline-wrapper" class="section-wrapper">
            <h1>Hello,<br />
                I'm Tim,<br />
                <span>Freelance Developer.</span><br />
            </h1>
            <p id="subtitle"><span>3D</span><span class="separator">|</span><span>digital experiences</span><span
                    class="separator">|</span><span>front-end development</span></p>
            <div class="message-buttons">
                <button class="message-button animated" data-animation="message" tabindex="1">get in touch</button>
                <button class="linkedin-button animated" data-animation="linkedin" tabindex="2"><i
                        class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i>connect on
                    LinkedIn</button>
            </div>
            <a class="animated link-with-icon" id="about-button" data-animation="about" tabindex="3" href="#"><i
                    class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-right"></i><span>learn more</span></a>
        </div>
        <div id="message-wrapper" class="section-wrapper">
            <div>
                <a class="back-arrow" data-animation="headline" tabindex="1" href="#"><i
                        class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-left"></i></a>
            </div>
            <div id="message-form-wrapper">
                <h2>Let's have a chat.</h2>
                <form novalidate>
                    <div class="field-wrapper">
                        <span>
                            <input placeholder="Name" name="name" tabindex="2" autocomplete="on" id="name-input" />
                            <span></span>
                            <input placeholder="Email" name="emailaddress" type="email" tabindex="3" autocomplete="on"
                                id="emailaddress-input" />
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-wrapper">
                        <input placeholder="Subject" name="subject" autocomplete="off" tabindex="4"
                            id="subject-input" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-wrapper" id="textarea-wrapper">
                        <textarea placeholder="Message" name="message" autocomplete="off" tabindex="5"
                            id="message-input"></textarea>

                    </div>
                    <div class="field-wrapper" id="submit-button-wrapper">
                        <button id="send-button" type="submit" tabindex="6"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-wrapper hide" id="invalid-input-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                        <p>Please fill out all the fields.</p>
                    </div>
                    <input class="honey" placeholder="Phone" name="phone" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="no" type="tel" />
                    <input class="honey" placeholder="Website" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="no"
                        type="url" />
                    <input class="honey" placeholder="Email" name="email" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="no"
                        type="email" />
                </form>
                <div id="message-confirmation">
                    <div id="message-success">
                        <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i>
                        <h3>Thank you for your message.</h3>
                        <p>I'll get back to you as soon as possible!</p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="message-client-error">
                        <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
                        <h3>400 (Bad Request)</h3>
                        <p>The server has rejected the data you entered.<br />Please try again later.<br />Sorry for the
                            inconvenience.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="message-server-error">
                        <i class="fas fa-redo-alt"></i>
                        <h3>400 (Internal Server Error)</h3>
                        <p>Uh. Oh. Something went wrong.<br />Please try again later.<br />Sorry for the inconvenience.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="message-unknown-error">
                        <i class="fas fa-redo-alt"></i>
                        <h3>Uh. Oh. Something went wrong.</h3>
                        <p>Please try again later.<br />Sorry for the inconvenience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="about-wrapper" class="section-wrapper">
            <div>
                <a class="back-arrow" data-animation="headline" tabindex="1" href="#"><i
                        class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-left"></i></a>
            </div>
            <div id="about-content">
                <h2>Tim Konieczny.</h2>
                <p lang="en">
                    My main areas of expertise are <b>computer graphics</b>, <b>digital experiences</b> and <b>front-end
                        development</b>.
                </p>
                <p lang="en">
                    I specialize in <b>all things 3D</b> and love creating <b>compelling user experiences</b> through
                    <b>animations</b> and <b>transitions</b>.
                </p>
                <p lang="en">
                    I focus on <b>small and medium web applications</b>. My experience ranges from 3D technologies like
                    <b class="no-hyphenation">WebGL</b>, <b class="no-hyphenation">three.js</b>, <b>shaders</b> and <b
                        class="no-hyphenation">WebXR</b>, to front-end technologies like <b
                        class="no-hyphenation">React</b>, <b class="no-hyphenation">Redux</b>, <b
                        class="no-hyphenation">HTML</b>, <b class="no-hyphenation">CSS</b> and <b
                        class="no-hyphenation">JavaScript</b>.
                </p>
                <p lang="en">
                    I can also help you with <b>native <span class="no-hyphenation">Android</span> development</b>,
                    including both <b>UI-driven apps</b> and <b>computer graphics projects</b> using <b
                        class="no-hyphenation">OpenGL ES</b>.
                </p>
                <p lang="en">
                    <b>I’m always excited to tackle interesting projects and collaborate with great people. Sounds good?
                        Let’s have a chat!</b>
                </p>
                <div class="message-buttons">
                    <button class="message-button" data-animation="message" tabindex="2">
                        get in touch
                    </button>
                    <button class="linkedin-button" data-animation="linkedin" tabindex="3">
                        <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i>connect on LinkedIn
                    </button>
                </div>
                <a id="privacy-policy-button" class="animated link-with-icon" data-animation="privacyPolicy"
                    tabindex="4" href="#"><i class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-right"></i><span>privacy policy and legal
                        information</span></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="privacy-policy-wrapper" class="section-wrapper">
            <div>
                <a class="back-arrow" data-animation="headline" tabindex="1" href="#"><i
                        class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-left"></i></a>
            </div>
            <div id="privacy-policy-content">
                <h2>About this website.</h2>
                <h3>Privacy policy</h3>
                <p lang="en">
                    This website uses Google Analytics, a service which transmits website traffic data to Google
                    servers. This instance of Google Analytics does not identify individual users or associate your IP
                    address with any other data held by Google. Reports provided by Google Analytics are used to help
                    understand website traffic and webpage usage. You may opt out of this tracking at any time by
                    activating the “Do Not Track” setting in your browser.
                </p>
                <h3>Legal information</h3>
                <p lang="en">
                    Tim Konieczny<br />
                    <span class="reverse"><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.street %></span><br />
                    <span class="reverse"><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.city %></span><br />
                    <span class="reverse"><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.country %></span><br />
                    Phone: <span class="reverse"><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.phone %></span><br />
                    Email: <span class="reverse"><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.email %></span>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>